Bill SCHUETTE, Attorney General of Michigan, et al., petitioners,
v.
FEDERAL ENERGY REGULATORY COMMISSION. No. 13-443. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 24, 2014.

Case below, Illinois Commerce Com'n v. Federal Energy Regulatory Com'n, 721 F.3d 764.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit denied.
